column2: "Not bad. But I wonder if that was too easy, even for a rookie like you."
"Hey, don't let go thinking you're something special just because I praised you a little!"
"I'm what's called an ARKS Watcher, and I've had my eye on you. Based on what I've seen, I'd say you were about second from the bottom."
"Whenever you want to try and prove yourself, come talk to me."
